        @PreAuthorize(value="hasRole(\'ROLE_MANAGER\')")
 @GetMapping(value="/all")
public java.util.List<ResultShiftDto> getAllShifts(@RequestParam(value="fromStartHour",defaultValue="0",required=false)
                                                                                                                               int fromStartHour,
                                                                                                                               @RequestParam(value="fromStartMinute",defaultValue="0",required=false)
                                                                                                                               int fromStartMinute,
                                                                                                                               @RequestParam(value="toEndHour",defaultValue="23",required=false)
                                                                                                                               int toEndHour,
                                                                                                                               @RequestParam(value="toEndMinute",defaultValue="59",required=false)
                                                                                                                               int toEndMinute)
        Gets all shifts in the database. Only a manager can access this endpoint. Takes search params that are given in integers for a 24-hour clock.
        Parameters:
        fromStartHour - the beginning hour of the search request. Defaults to 0 (12am)
        fromStartMinute - the beginning minute of the search request. Defaults to 0
        toEndHour - the end hour of the search request. Defaults to 23 (11pm)
        toEndMinute - the end hour of the search request. Defaults to 59
        Returns:
        A list of ResultShiftDto shifts
